<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Paws & Hearts Pet Adoption</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        nav a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        
        .hero {
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url("/api/placeholder/1200/400");
            height: 400px;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        
        .features {
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .feature-cards {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 300px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .card-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .modules {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .module-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .module-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        
        .module-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .module-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .user-icon::after {
            content: "üë§";
        }
        
        .admin-icon::after {
            content: "üîë";
        }
        
        .volunteer-icon::after {
            content: "ü§ù";
        }
        
        .doctor-icon::after {
            content: "‚öïÔ∏è";
        }
        
        .pets {
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .pet-gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .pet-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        
        .pet-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .pet-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .pet-info {
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        
        .pet-info h3 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .pet-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .footer-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .feature-cards, .module-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .pet-gallery {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            }
            
            nav a {
                float: none;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Paws & Hearts Pet Adoption</h1>
        <p>Find your perfect furry companion</p>
    </header>
    
    <nav>
        <a href="/adminLoginPage">Admin</a>
        <a href="/users">Buy Pets</a>
        <a href="/seller">Add Your Pets</a>
        <a href="/login">Health Care</a>
        <a href="/consultant">Volunteers </a>
        <a href="#login" style="float: right;">Login</a>
        <a href="#register" style="float: right;">Register</a>
    </nav>
    
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Give a Pet a Forever Home</h1>
            <p>Our mission is to find loving homes for abandoned and rescued animals. Join us in making a difference in their lives.</p>
            <a href="#pets" class="btn">Adopt Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features" id="about">
        <h2>Why Adopt With Us?</h2>
        <div class="feature-cards">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/016/928/537/non_2x/pet-care-logo-icon-isolated-free-vector.jpg" alt="Healthy Pets">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Healthy Pets</h3>
                    <p>All our pets are examined by licensed veterinarians and receive necessary vaccinations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/016/928/537/non_2x/pet-care-logo-icon-isolated-free-vector.jpg" alt="Support System">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Ongoing Support</h3>
                    <p>Our team of volunteers and veterinarians will support you throughout your pet adoption journey.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/016/928/537/non_2x/pet-care-logo-icon-isolated-free-vector.jpg" alt="Community">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Join Our Community</h3>
                    <p>Become part of a loving community of pet owners who share tips and experiences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="modules" id="modules">
        <h2>Our Modules</h2>
        <p>Different roles to help our adoption process run smoothly</p>
        <div class="module-container">
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-icon user-icon"></div>
                <h3>User Module</h3>
                <p>Browse available pets, submit adoption applications, and track your application status.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:5000/users/login" class="btn" style="margin-top: 1rem;">User Portal</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-icon admin-icon"></div>
                <h3>Admin Module</h3>
                <p>Manage shelter operations, approve adoptions, and oversee the entire system.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:5000/adminLoginPage" class="btn" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Admin Portal</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-icon volunteer-icon"></div>
                <h3>Volunteer Module</h3>
                <p>Coordinate volunteer activities, schedule pet care, and organize adoption events.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:5000/consultant" class="btn" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Volunteer Portal</a>
            </div>
            <div class="module-card">
                <div class="module-icon doctor-icon"></div>
                <h3>Doctor Module</h3>
                <p>Manage pet health records, schedule check-ups, and provide medical advice.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:5000/login" class="btn" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Doctor Portal</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
